publisher			Adult Swim Games							
publish_time	 2015年7月9日		
desc_long							评测						8.5 – IGN Sweden“Traverser is one of those indie gems that is truly worthy of the adjective 'gem'”A – Gaming Goddess“Add the logic puzzles, the intoxicating boss fights, and the ability to throw garbage around willy nilly (seriously), and you’ve got the recipe for an exciting, engaging experience.”Sound on Sight												关于这款游戏							The sun has died, forcing mankind to retreat towards what little heat remains beneath the planet's surface. Humanity's last bastion, Brimstone, is a city literally divided into upper and lower classes, both controlled by the all-powerful Raven Corporation. Raven Corp also controls the city's breathable air, with the wealthy Upper City getting far more than its fair share…Young Valerie Bennett has just passed the test to become a Traverser; a new kind of peacekeeper with the ability to travel between the Upper and Lower cities of Brimstone. Join her on a mission to reveal Raven Corp's sinister secrets, uncover years of lies and propaganda, and discover the most dangerous thing in all of Brimstone: the truth.Features         3D adventure with hand-drawn 2D effects          Manipulate objects with your Gravity Glove to solve puzzles and navigate the dangerous city of Brimstone         Use "Flip Stations" to traverse between Brimstone's Upper and Lower sides     						
